No, it's a gentle kick; you're doing it wrong.

269
00:11:18,387 --> 00:11:20,103
来 把东西都给我
Here. Give me those.

270
00:11:27,195 --> 00:11:29,529
是不是要绕一个圈?
Uh, maybe it was more of a circle?

271
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:35,368
那人以为你们是一对儿真是太奇怪了
It's weird that guy thought you were a couple.

272
00:11:36,154 --> 00:11:37,320
