346
00:14:46,177 --> 00:14:48,561
我已经疼到看不了动画...
I'm in too much pain to watch cartoo...

347
00:14:48,563 --> 00:14:51,064
喔! 这集不错
Oh! This is a good one.

348
00:14:51,683 --> 00:14:52,982
我照顾他的时间
I've been babysitting him

349
00:14:52,984 --> 00:14:54,684
可是比你长得多了
way longer than you have.

350
00:14:56,238 --> 00:15:00,023
好吧 不就一辆破车嘛 买就买
Fine. I'll buy the stupid van.

351
00:15:02,193 --> 00:15:04,360
这是我吃过的味道最好的薄饼了
This is the best blintz I've ever had.

352
00:15:04,362 --> 00:15:05,912
谢谢你
Oh. Thank you.

353
00:15:05,914 --> 00:15:08,498
这已经把之前那尴尬的转折
It almost makes up for the incredibly awkward turn

354
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:10,533
弥补得差不多了
things took earlier.

355
00:15:12,003 --> 00:15:14,037
我... 我想我还是先走了
You know what, I... I think I'm just gonna go.

356
00:15:14,039 --> 00:15:15,922
别 Stuart 别走啊
No, Stuart, don't.

357
00:15:15,924 --> 00:15:18,625
不... 我把你和Sheldon当作我的家人
No, I... I consider you and Sheldon like my family,

358
00:15:18,627 --> 00:15:21,127
但我都拿不准你们是不是把我当朋友
and I'm not even sure you think of me as a friend.

359
00:15:21,129 --> 00:15:23,379
你知道这是什么感觉吗?
You have any idea how that feels?

360
00:15:23,381 --> 00:15:25,882
我们很抱歉
We're so sorry.

361
00:15:25,884 --> 00:15:28,051
每个人都是最后才会想起我
I'm always the last one anybody thinks of.

362
00:15:28,053 --> 00:15:29,686
不是这样的
Well, no, that's not true.

363
00:15:29,688 --> 00:15:32,188
有的时候大家最后才想起Koothrappali
I mean, sometimes it's Koothrappali.

364
00:15:33,224 --> 00:15:35,358
但说出来又不好
But we're not supposed to say that 'cause

365
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:37,393
因为他不受大众喜爱
he's a minority.

366
00:15:37,395 --> 00:15:38,444
再见
Bye.

367
00:15:38,446 --> 00:15:40,563
Stuart 等等
Stuart, wait.

368
00:15:42,033 --> 00:15:44,784
我知道被人忽视和遗忘的滋味
I do know what it feels like to be left out.

369
00:15:44,786 --> 00:15:46,402
我也知道
I know how it feels, too.

370
00:15:46,404 --> 00:15:49,405
行了 这是我和他之间的事 你一边儿凉快去
All right, this is about me and him; you're not part of it.

371
00:15:51,242 --> 00:15:54,577
Stuart 或许我们是有点不重视你了
Stuart, perhaps we do take you for granted,

372
00:15:54,579 --> 00:15:56,379
这样做是不对的
and that is not acceptable.

373
00:15:56,381 --> 00:15:59,332
但请相信你确实是我们圈子里
Please know that you truly are a valuable member

374
00:15:59,334 --> 00:16:00,633
珍贵的一员
of our social group.

375
00:16:00,635 --> 00:16:02,418
谢谢
Thank you.

376
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:05,388
好了 我提议大家举杯
You know, in fact, I'd like to propose a toast.

377
00:16:08,893 --> 00:16:10,009
敬Stuart
To Stuart.

378
00:16:10,011 --> 00:16:12,428
一个好人
A fine man,

379
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:16,149
一个好朋友 一个很棒的客人
a good friend and a wonderful guest.

380
00:16:16,151 --> 00:16:18,101
说的是 干杯
Hear, hear. Cheers.

381
00:16:18,103 --> 00:16:21,821
干杯 于录音棚观众之前拍摄
Cheers. Filmed before a live studio audience.

382
00:16:25,410 --> 00:16:28,945
这就是一个患有哮喘的矮子科学家
And that is how a short asthmatic scientist

383
00:16:28,947 --> 00:16:31,581
攻陷了一个冰山美人的故事
landed a stone cold fox.

384
00:16:31,583 --> 00:16:33,583
哇哦
Oh. Whoa.

385
00:16:35,337 --> 00:16:37,620
我简直难以想象你可以向同一个人
I didn't know you can propose to the same person

386
00:16:37,622 --> 00:16:39,672
求那么多次婚
so many times.

387
00:16:39,674 --> 00:16:42,258
第三次我是用空中写字求的婚
The third time, I did it in skywriting,

388
00:16:42,260 --> 00:16:43,876
但她头都没抬一下
but she never looked up.

389
00:16:44,679 --> 00:16:46,429
还有一次 是我跟他求的婚
You know, once, I proposed to him.

390
00:16:46,431 --> 00:16:48,381
是啊 我拒绝了
Yeah. I said no.

391
00:16:48,383 --> 00:16:49,716
为什么?
Why?

392
00:16:49,718 --> 00:16:51,934
我就是想让她多费点事儿
I just wanted to make her work for it.

393
00:16:52,721 --> 00:16:55,638
没事 我们秋后算账
Yeah, that's gonna cost you later.

394
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:58,641
等等 她和你在一起是因为你有钱吗?
Hang on. Is she just with you because you're rich?

395
00:16:58,643 --> 00:17:00,560
她赚的比我多了去了!
She makes more money than I do!

396
00:17:00,562 --> 00:17:02,945
什么? 你也太强了吧!
What?! Who are you?!

397
00:17:11,828 --> 00:17:13,911
你知道我还喜欢你什么吗?
Do you know what else I love about you?

398
00:17:13,913 --> 00:17:14,962
什么?
Hmm?

399
00:17:14,964 --> 00:17:19,083
你... 的书法 简直无懈可击!
Y... Your handwriting is impeccable!

400
00:17:19,085 --> 00:17:20,334
谢谢你能注意到这个!
Thank you for noticing!

401
00:17:20,336 --> 00:17:22,003
我说真的 我说真的
No, I mean it. I mean it.

402
00:17:22,005 --> 00:17:25,423
你就仿佛拥有标签机的灵魂
It's like you have the soul of a label maker.

403
00:17:26,275 --> 00:17:27,927
你知道我喜欢你什么吗?
You know what I love about you?

404
00:17:27,951 --> 00:17:28,810
什么?
Hmm?

405
00:17:28,811 --> 00:17:31,345
你出门一定会随身携带回形针!
You never leave the house without a paper clip!

406
00:17:32,181 --> 00:17:34,098
你永远不知道什么时候就会出现两张纸
You never know when two pieces of paper

407
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:37,902
需要临时在左上角固定起来
might temporarily need fastening in the top left corner.

408
00:17:41,074 --> 00:17:44,358
我还喜欢你从来不说脏话
I also love how you never use swear words.

409
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:45,776
事实证明嘛
You know, it turns out,

410
00:17:45,778 --> 00:17:49,914
不说脏话 你也一样可以伤人于无形
you can hurt people just as well without 'em.

411
00:17:51,951 --> 00:17:54,869
有没有人来帮我收拾收拾这些东西啊
Maybe I can get a little help putting some of this stuff away.

412
00:17:54,871 --> 00:17:56,871
淡定
Oh, calm down.

413
00:17:56,873 --> 00:17:59,006
我已经 "收拾" 了五杯这个了
I already put away five of these!

414
00:17:59,008 --> 00:18:01,542
看见了吗?
You see?

415
00:18:01,544 --> 00:18:04,712
开口没脏话 文明你我他
No muss, no fuss, not a single cuss.
